tags: steve rogers x plus size reader
body:
HEY GALS!!!

I might be back!!! I’ve been hella busy and you know found a nigga who is rocking my world (we aren’t dating and it’s a long story but he’s a mess also I called him a nigga when he’s most definitely a half Caucasian half Hispanic fool) and I’ve had absolutely no desire to write but going back and re reading comments made me want to do it again so here’s the schedule kiddos

1. I got a request for a Brockhampton fic and honestly I lost my previous requests I spent hours trying to find so imma just uh make it up to them with this one? (I don’t mean to be shitty I’m very unorganized so welcome to the pit of frustration that is liking me as a writer)

2. I miss my black panther family tew much. And so it’s time. TO MAKE THE FOURTH PART OF LAID UP!!!! This the damn Baby Daddy Edition. Yep y’all are about to experience me struggling through writing a pregnancy fic. Y’all ain’t ready (nigga I ain’t either)

3. SETBACKS AND TATTOOS!!! It’s honestly so good. And I feel bad bc it really needs to be finished so I’m gonna work on trying to get a 2,000 word chapter out. Gotta feed my babes with some Steve and Bucky daddy-ness

4. LIFT!!! So for some reason lift and setbacks are super popular but their second parts and other chapters aren’t getting anywhere near the same amount of reads and my readers keep asking me “Where’s part 2” and I keep putting links but idk some versions of my writing have the link and some do not it’s annoying but whatever. So I’m probably gonna wrap lift up in 1 or 2 more chapters it’s shouldn’t be that hard to finish I figure

5. I’ll officially open up requests. Honestly I feel like I’m too distracted by this man I’m in love with so writing in my free time will tune him out of my life. Plus I’m thiiiiiiiissssclosetowhoopinghisass bc he ain’t shit. Also bc he found out I’m a writer and keeps tryna play me but whatever.

PLEASE BE PATIENT WITH ME THIS WEEK‼️‼️

I have a lot going on. Like A LOT. I’m doing hair rn for my aunt then I gotta go to my grandmas house and help cook for thanksgiving (it takes her 4 days bc we have about 70 family members coming back and forth and whew chile the cookin) then I gotta do my hair and my cousins keep bothering me to hang out and I got hw and all that shit I gotta practice (yes ya college cutie is in band I play oboe for concert band and sax for marching and jazz not important tho) so yes I’m always busy and I apologize for that.

ALRIGHT KIDDOS THAT IS ALL

@killmongersgurl @killmoncoochie @texasbama @purple-apricots @inlovewithmakeupcomicsanimelove @muse-of-mbaku @504queen

@lionheartsthings @abschaffer2 @scrumptiouslytenaciouscrusade @myboyfriendgiriboy @misspooh @sicksadgen @lunaerly

@awkwardlyabstract @wawakanda-btch @eriknutinthispoosy @erikslulbaby

title: POW! Entertainment risponde ai commenti di Bill Maher su Stan Lee
body:
POW! Entertainment risponde ai commenti di Bill Maher su Stan Lee

La POW! Entertainment ha rilasciato una dichiarazione in risposta ai commenti offensivi rilasciati da Bill Maher sul suo blog a proposito di Stan Lee, della sua eredità ed dei fan del mondo dei fumetti che ha contribuito a creare.

Stan Leeè morto all’età di 95 anni lo scorso lunedì dopo una serie di problemi di salute lungo tutto il passato ultimo anno che lo hanno costretto a iniziare a saltare…
